    {
      "text": "Computerspiel",
      "lang": "de",
      "source": "wikidata"
    },
    {
      "text": "Virtual Kasparov is a chess video game developed by Titus Interactive Studio, published by Titus Interactive and distributed in Europe by Virgin Interactive for the PlayStation and Game Boy Advance. Game can be played against beginners, novices, champions, or personality players. Games that Garry Kasparov played during his career, as well as interviews about his chess career, can be viewed in the game.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Virtual Kasparov est un jeu vidéo de jeu d'échecs sorti en 2002 sur PlayStation et Game Boy Advance. Le jeu a été édité par Titus.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Virtual Kasparov es un videojuego de ajedrez desarrollado y publicado por Titus Interactive en 2001-2002 para las plataformas PlayStation y Game Boy Advance. Virtual Kasparov fue distribuido en Europa por Virgin Interactive.",
      "lang": "es",
      "source": "wikipedia_es"
    },
    {
      "text": "Virtual Kasparov è un videogioco di scacchi sviluppato da Titus Interactive Studio, pubblicato da Titus Interactive e distribuito in Europa da Virgin Interactive per PlayStation e Game Boy Advance. Il gioco può essere giocato in modalità principiante, campione o contro giocatori reali. Le partite che Garry Kasparov ha giocato durante la sua carriera, così come le interviste sulla sua carriera di scacchi, possono essere visualizzati nel gioco.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "«Virtual Kasparov» — компьютерная программа для игры в шахматы, распространяемая в Европе компанией Virgin Interactive для PlayStation и Game Boy Advance.",
      "lang": "ru",
      "source": "wikipedia_ru"
    },
    {
      "text": "『バーチャル・カスパロフ』は、Titus Interactive Studioが開発し、Titus Interactiveがパブリッシング、Virgin Interactiveがヨーロッパで流通させた、プレイステーションおよびゲームボーイアドバンス用チェスのビデオゲームです。初心者、初級者、チャンピオン、個性的なプレイヤーなど、様々な相手と対戦することができます。ゲーム内では、ガリ・カスパロフがキャリア中にプレイしたゲームや、彼のチェスキャリアに関するインタビューを視聴することが可能です。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
